-ARE YOU POSITIVE
THESE ARE THE TWO MEN
FROM LAST NIGHT?

28:14.649 --> 28:16.999
-YEAH.

28:17.130 --> 28:18.740
-HOW CAN YOU BE SURE
IF THEY WERE BOTH WEARING
SKI MASKS WHEN THEY BROKE IN?

28:18.871 --> 28:20.873
-THE ONE WITH
THE FRIZZY HAIR,
HE HAD MY LIGHTER.

28:21.743 --> 28:24.093
