MY GRANDFATHER
GAVE IT TO ME.

28:24.224 --> 28:25.791
YOU SAW IT.

28:25.921 --> 28:27.183
THAT'S WHAT I RECOGNIZED.

28:29.403 --> 28:31.013
-STAKEOUT AT SURFRIDER BEACH?

28:31.797 --> 28:33.320
-YEAH, IF I HAD
THE PERSONNEL.

28:34.016 --> 28:35.539
-YOU'RE LOOKING AT HIM.

28:35.670 --> 28:37.019
-MAN:
FIRST TEAM ON THE SET.

28:37.150 --> 28:39.195
-YEAH.
