SHE DOESN'T.

29:03.524 --> 29:04.960
-LENA: WHAT IS THE MEANING
OF THIS...

29:24.632 --> 29:26.634
-[LAUGHING]

29:30.420 --> 29:33.423
THAT'S MY BOY.
-YOU MUST BE PROUD.

29:34.120 --> 29:36.165
-WELL, SO FAR, SO GOOD.

29:36.296 --> 29:39.212
-YOU KNOW, IN A WAY,
MRS. TORZINI KIND OF
REMINDS ME OF MY MOM.

29:39.342 --> 29:41.344
-I'M SORRY,
I DON'T SEE THE RESEMBLANCE.

29:41.475 --> 29:43.390
-NO, IT'S THE WAY
SHE'S LOOKING AT GUIDO.

29:43.520 --> 29:45.784
