-AWESOME.

35:34.610 --> 35:36.786
-WELL, HE MUST HAVE
GOTTEN THAT FROM
THE OTHER SIDE OF THE FAMILY.

35:36.917 --> 35:37.918
-PROBABLY DID.

35:39.746 --> 35:40.877
WHAT DO YOU THINK
ABOUT THIS GIRL LENA?

35:41.008 --> 35:43.053
-PFF, SHE'S GORGEOUS.

35:44.316 --> 35:45.230
CHARMING...

35:46.144 --> 35:47.362
GENERALLY SEXY.

35:48.929 --> 35:50.452
YOU GONNA SEE HER TONIGHT?

35:52.106 --> 35:55.675
-YEAH, YEAH, I TOLD HER
I'D COME BY AND HELP HER
PACK UP THE REST OF HER THINGS.

35:55.805 --> 35:57.981
-DO YOU MIND
IF I TAG ALONG?

35:58.112 --> 36:00.506
I'D LIKE TO SIT DOWN
AND TALK WITH HER,

36:00.636 --> 36:02.986
SEE IF SHE REMEMBERS
ANYTHING ELSE ABOUT THOSE GUYS.

36:04.597 --> 36:05.989
-NO PROBLEM, PAL.
LET'S GO.

36:08.514 --> 36:09.993
-IT'S TIME TO GO
VISIT OUR ACTRESS.

36:10.124 --> 36:11.517
HER DECK LOOKED
SLIPPERY TO ME.

36:11.647 --> 36:13.649
-YEAH, REAL EASY TO FALL OFF.

36:15.216 --> 36:16.913
-ROCKS BELOW, BRUTAL.

36:17.044 --> 36:18.437
-[BOTH LAUGHING]

36:18.567 --> 36:20.526
-WOOHOO.

36:33.582 --> 36:35.454
-NO! NO.

36:37.325 --> 36:40.372
[GRUNTING]

36:56.910 --> 36:57.737
-THIS IS THE VAN, MITCH.

37:07.268 --> 37:09.183
-I'LL TAKE THE SIDE.

37:15.972 --> 37:17.670
-YOU GONNA TALK, HUH?

37:47.265 --> 37:50.050
DON'T MOVE
AND DON'T MAKE A SOUND.

38:06.849 --> 38:08.677
-[GLASS SHATTERS]
-WHAT WAS THAT?

38:08.808 --> 38:12.246
-OOH. MM-MM.

38:15.293 --> 38:16.511
-OH, MAN, LET'S SPLIT.

38:17.991 --> 38:19.209
-WE CAN'T.
SHE'LL TALK, MAN.

38:29.263 --> 38:31.134
-WHAT ARE WE
GONNA DO, BRO?

38:41.710 --> 38:43.756
-HEY, LET'S GET RID OF HER.

38:45.105 --> 38:47.194
-[MUFFLED SCREAMS]

39:20.923 --> 39:22.664
-GUIDO, GUIDO.

39:22.795 --> 39:23.839
-MAMA.

39:25.580 --> 39:27.800
MAMA, I GOT SOMETHING
TO TELL YOU.

39:27.930 --> 39:29.410
I'M NOT REALLY A LIFEGUARD.

39:30.106 --> 39:31.630
-OH, I KNOW.

39:32.544 --> 39:33.936
-YOU KNOW?
HOW DO YOU KNOW?

39:34.676 --> 39:38.027
-GUIDO, WHEN ARE YOU
GONNA LEARN YOU CAN'T
FOOL MAMA?

39:39.638 --> 39:41.466
-CAN YOU EVER FIND IT
IN YOUR HEART TO FORGIVE ME?

39:42.597 --> 39:45.470
-GUIDO, YOU'RE MY BABY.

39:45.600 --> 39:48.560
I'LL ALWAYS LOVE YOU
NO MATTER WHAT YOU DO.

39:49.822 --> 39:50.910
BESIDES...

39:52.215 --> 39:55.480
WE ALL TELL LITTLE WHITE LIES
EVERY ONCE IN A WHILE.

39:57.220 --> 39:59.353
FOR INSTANCE,

39:59.484 --> 40:00.920
IN MY LETTER,

40:01.050 --> 40:03.662
I SAID THIS WAS GONNA BE
A SHORT TRIP.

40:05.577 --> 40:07.492
THAT WASN'T
EXACTLY TRUE.

40:07.622 --> 40:09.058
-IT WASN'T?

40:13.236 --> 40:15.413
-I'VE COME TO LIVE WITH YOU.

40:18.677 --> 40:19.982
-MAMA.

40:20.896 --> 40:22.158
-GUIDO.

40:25.423 --> 40:28.600
[SIGHS]

40:34.475 --> 40:36.477
-ANOTHER DAY,
ANOTHER DOLLAR.

40:39.611 --> 40:41.439
-50 CENTS AFTER TAXES.

40:43.789 --> 40:45.443
WHAT'S HAPPENING
WITH YOU AND LENA?

40:46.879 --> 40:50.273
-SHE'S GOING BACK TO ITALY
TOMORROW, AFTER SHE FINISHES
SHOOTING HER FILM.

40:52.711 --> 40:54.452
I GUESS L.A. WAS
TOO MUCH FOR HER.

40:55.191 --> 40:57.106
-EASY COME, EASY GO.

40:58.978 --> 41:00.893
-GUESS IT WASN'T
MEANT TO BE.

41:02.111 --> 41:04.244
-WELL, THAT'S THE STORY
OF MY LIFE.

41:05.854 --> 41:09.423
-DO I SENSE A LITTLE BIT
OF DATELESSNESS
ON YOUR PART, THIS EVENING?

41:10.772 --> 41:13.035
-GOT A CALL
AROUND LUNCHTIME.

41:14.036 --> 41:16.299
HER CAT IS SICK.

41:17.953 --> 41:19.607
-HAVING A CAT SCAN, EH?

41:19.738 --> 41:21.566
-[BOTH LAUGHING]

41:23.263 --> 41:24.786
-WELL, IF IT'S
ANY CONSOLATION,

41:24.917 --> 41:27.963
THE WIZ KID IS COOKING
VEAL SCALLOPINI TONIGHT.

41:29.008 --> 41:31.576
YOU'RE INVITED.
-VEAL SCALLOPINI?

41:31.706 --> 41:33.708
HE DOESN'T MESS AROUND.

41:33.839 --> 41:36.319
-WHAT CAN I SAY?
THE KID'S A CULINARY GENIUS.

41:38.104 --> 41:39.497
-YOU SURE HE'S
NOT ADOPTED?

41:41.411 --> 41:44.763
-YOU WANT HIM?
-OH, NO. [LAUGHS]

41:44.893 --> 41:46.895
LET'S GET OUT OF HERE.

42:05.087 --> 42:07.350
[ENDING MUSIC]
